Judy Lewis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Judy_Lewis 0 Judy Lewis (born Judith Young; November 6, 1935 – November 25, 2011) was an American actress, writer, producer, and therapist. She was the secret biological daughter of actor Clark Gable and actress Loretta Young.
